{This is a typical Catalan game with Nc3.} 1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nf3 d5 4. g3
h6 5. Bg2 Bd6 6. O-O O-O 7. Nc3 Nc6 8. b3 dxc4 (8... Re8 9. Bb2 dxc4 10. bxc4
e5 {Transposes to the game.}) 9. bxc4 e5 10. Bb2 (10. e3 exd4 (10... Re8 {
Is the most accurate move.}) 11. exd4 Re8 {The pawn pushes c4-c5 and d4-d5 may
look dangerous, but in fact, they are not.} 12. c5 Bf8 $11 13. d5 $2 Nb4 $17)
10... Re8 11. Nb5 (11. c5 {Almost always Black meets c4-c5 with ...exd4!} exd4
12. cxd6 dxc3 13. Bxc3 Ne4 $1 $17 {[%csl Rc3,Rd6][%cal Gd8d6]} (13... cxd6 $15
{White has some compensation for the pawn.})) 11... e4 $1 12. Ne5 a6 13. Nxc6
bxc6 14. Nxd6 cxd6 15. d5 c5 $1 16. Qc2 Bf5 (16... Qe7 $6 17. Bxf6 $16) 17. Qc3
Rb8 18. e3 Qd7 19. Rfb1 Bg4 20. Qc2 Nh7 21. h4 Bf3 22. Qc3 Nf6 23. Qe1 Bxg2 24.
Kxg2 Ng4 25. Qe2 Rb4 26. Bc3 Ra4 27. Rb3 Qf5 28. a3 Rxc4 29. Rab1 h5 30. Kg1
Rxc3 31. Rxc3 Ne5 32. Qf1 Nf3+ 33. Kh1 Nd2 34. Qd1 Qh3+ 0-1

